The '''Purple Worm''', also known as simply '''WORM''', is an enemy in the original ''[[Final Fantasy]]'' found in the [[Chaos Shrine (Final Fantasy)|Chaos Shrine]], and is a dangerous enemy when fought in groups. It is advised to kill off any other enemies that are accompanying the worm, then focus on defeating the worm using strong physical attacks and spells.



